node.title: Medical Council deregisters Canterbury doctor for giving out medical certificates as vaccine exemptions
node.content: ["The Medical Council has confirmed Jonie Girouard, the Canterbury GP Newshub filmed giving out bogus COVID-19 vaccine exemptions, can no longer practise in New Zealand.", "\"Council can confirm that Jonie Girouard is no longer listed as registered and able to practise in New Zealand,\" chair Curtis Walker told the NZ Herald.", "More to come."]
